      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Chapter 4: Namespaces = Different Cargo Zones\n\n\n\n    KubeSagar Logistics huge company थियो.\n    सबै सामान एउटै ठाउँमा राखे chaos हुन्थ्यो.\n    \n        त्यसैले different zones बनाइयो:\n        \n                dev\n                \n                test\n                \n                prod\n                \n                finance\n\n\n    Technical रूपमा यसलाई भनिन्छ:\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nNamespace\n\n     Analogy:\n    \n        Namespace = port ko different cargo yard / zone\n        \n            dev zone = practice सामान\n            \n            prod zone = live customer सामान\n            \n            kube-system = system staff area\n\n\n\n    Nepali मा:\n    \n        “Cluster bhitra ko छुट्टाछुट्टै area”",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Chapter 4: Namespaces = Different Cargo Zones\n\n\n\n    KubeSagar Logistics huge company थियो.\n    सबै सामान एउटै ठाउँमा राखे chaos हुन्थ्यो.\n    \n        त्यसैले different zones बनाइयो:\n        \n                dev\n                \n                test\n                \n                prod\n                \n                finance\n\n\n    Technical रूपमा यसलाई भनिन्छ:\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nNamespace\n\n     Analogy:\n    \n        Namespace = port ko different cargo yard / zone\n        \n            dev zone = practice सामान\n            \n            prod zone = live customer सामान\n            \n            kube-system = system staff area\n\n\n\n    Nepali मा:\n    \n        “Cluster bhitra ko छुट्टाछुट्टै area”",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
