      "text": "Chapter 5: Context = Your Access Badge\n\n    अब imagine गर, तिमी port manager हौ.\n    तिमीसँग access card छ.\n\n        त्यो card ले बताउँछ:\n        \n                कुन port मा जाने\n                \n                कुन role मा जाने\n                \n                कुन zone मा default काम गर्ने\n\n\n    Kubernetes मा यही हो:\n\n\n\n\nContext\n    Technical:\n    \n        A context contains:\n        \n                cluster\n                \n                user\n                \n                default namespace\n\n\n\nAnalogy:\n\n    Context = timro work badge / profile\n\n    Example:\n    \n            dev-ctx = same cluster + admin user + dev namespace\n            \n            prod-ctx = same cluster + admin user + prod namespace",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Chapter 5: Context = Your Access Badge\n\n    अब imagine गर, तिमी port manager हौ.\n    तिमीसँग access card छ.\n\n        त्यो card ले बताउँछ:\n        \n                कुन port मा जाने\n                \n                कुन role मा जाने\n                \n                कुन zone मा default काम गर्ने\n\n\n    Kubernetes मा यही हो:\n\n\n\n\nContext\n    Technical:\n    \n        A context contains:\n        \n                cluster\n                \n                user\n                \n                default namespace\n\n\n\nAnalogy:\n\n    Context = timro work badge / profile\n\n    Example:\n    \n            dev-ctx = same cluster + admin user + dev namespace\n            \n            prod-ctx = same cluster + admin user + prod namespace",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
