      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Chapter 7: ConfigMap and Secret\n\n\n    Company चलाउन documents पनि चाहिन्छ.\n\n\n\n\nConfigMap = Open Instruction Paper\n\n\n    जसमा secret नभएको config हुन्छ:\n    \n        port\n        \n        app mode\n        \n        feature flag\n\n\n\n    Analogy:\n    \n    ConfigMap = खुल्ला instruction sheet\n\n\n\n\n\nSecret = Locked Locker\n\n\n    Sensitive सामान:\n    \n        password\n        \n        token\n        \n        certificate\n        \n        key\n    \n    \n    Analogy:\n    \n        Secret = locked envelope / secure locker",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Chapter 7: ConfigMap and Secret\n\n\n    Company चलाउन documents पनि चाहिन्छ.\n\n\n\n\nConfigMap = Open Instruction Paper\n\n\n    जसमा secret नभएको config हुन्छ:\n    \n        port\n        \n        app mode\n        \n        feature flag\n\n\n\n    Analogy:\n    \n    ConfigMap = खुल्ला instruction sheet\n\n\n\n\n\nSecret = Locked Locker\n\n\n    Sensitive सामान:\n    \n        password\n        \n        token\n        \n        certificate\n        \n        key\n    \n    \n    Analogy:\n    \n        Secret = locked envelope / secure locker",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
