      "updated": 1773806344397,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Chapter 8: Storage\n\n    Some cargo temporary हुन्छ, some permanent.\n\n\n\nVolume\n\n    Pod को storage area\n\n\n        Analogy:\n        \n            Volume = ship भित्रको small storage room\n\n\n\n\nPersistentVolume (PV)\n\n    Long-term reserved storage\n\n\n        Analogy:\n        \n            PV = port ko warehouse\n\n\n\n\n\n\nPersistentVolumeClaim (PVC)\n\n    Storage माग्ने request\n\n\n        Analogy:\n        \n            PVC = warehouse booking form",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Chapter 8: Storage\n\n    Some cargo temporary हुन्छ, some permanent.\n\n\n\nVolume\n\n    Pod को storage area\n\n\n        Analogy:\n        \n            Volume = ship भित्रको small storage room\n\n\n\n\nPersistentVolume (PV)\n\n    Long-term reserved storage\n\n\n        Analogy:\n        \n            PV = port ko warehouse\n\n\n\n\n\n\nPersistentVolumeClaim (PVC)\n\n    Storage माग्ने request\n\n\n        Analogy:\n        \n            PVC = warehouse booking form",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
