      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Chapter 9: Self-Healing Magic\n\n\n    KubeSagar company को biggest power थियो:\n\n\n\n    यदि एउटा cargo container समुद्रमा खस्यो भने,\n    company human लाई wait नगरिकन तुरुन्त new cargo तयार गर्थ्यो.\n\n\n    \n    Technical रूपमा:\n    \n        pod crash? recreate\n        \n        node down? reschedule if possible\n        \n        desired != actual? reconcile\n    \n\n\n    Analogy:\n    \n        Self-healing = automatic replacement system",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Chapter 9: Self-Healing Magic\n\n\n    KubeSagar company को biggest power थियो:\n\n\n\n    यदि एउटा cargo container समुद्रमा खस्यो भने,\n    company human लाई wait नगरिकन तुरुन्त new cargo तयार गर्थ्यो.\n\n\n    \n    Technical रूपमा:\n    \n        pod crash? recreate\n        \n        node down? reschedule if possible\n        \n        desired != actual? reconcile\n    \n\n\n    Analogy:\n    \n        Self-healing = automatic replacement system",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
