      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1773806684260,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Practical CKA-Style Mini Scenario\n\n\n\nअब एउटा exam-style story बनाऔं.\n\n\n\nLuke port operator ले एउटा cluster manage गर्दैछ.\nउसलाई dev zone मा एउटा web app launch गर्नुछ.\n\n\n\n\n\nRequirements:\n\n        namespace = dev\n        \n        deployment name = web-app\n        \n        image = nginx\n        \n        replicas = 3\n        \n        expose through a service named web-svc\n\n\n\n\n\nअब question-answer format मा:\n\n\n\nQ1. First dev zone create गर्न command के हो?\nAnswer:\nkubectl create namespace dev\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ2. Current context को default namespace dev बनाउन command के हो?\nAnswer:\nkubectl config set-context --current --namespace=dev\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ3. nginx image ko 3 replicas भएको deployment बनाउने command?\nAnswer:\nkubectl create deployment web-app --image=nginx -n dev\nkubectl scale deployment web-app --replicas=3 -n dev\n\nAlternative:\n\nkubectl create deployment web-app --image=nginx --replicas=3 -n dev\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ4. web app expose गर्न service command?\nAnswer:\nkubectl expose deployment web-app --name=web-svc --port=80 \n--target-port=80 -n dev\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ5. कुन component decides where these 3 pods will run?\nAnswer:\n\nkube-scheduler\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ6. कुन component actually node मा pod run गराउँछ?\nAnswer:\n\nkubelet, using container runtime\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ7. कुन component stores this deployment record?\nAnswer:\n\netcd\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ8. User traffic service बाट सही pod मा कसले route गर्छ?\nAnswer:\n\nkube-proxy",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Practical CKA-Style Mini Scenario\n\n\n\nअब एउटा exam-style story बनाऔं.\n\n\n\nLuke port operator ले एउटा cluster manage गर्दैछ.\nउसलाई dev zone मा एउटा web app launch गर्नुछ.\n\n\n\n\n\nRequirements:\n\n        namespace = dev\n        \n        deployment name = web-app\n        \n        image = nginx\n        \n        replicas = 3\n        \n        expose through a service named web-svc\n\n\n\n\n\nअब question-answer format मा:\n\n\n\nQ1. First dev zone create गर्न command के हो?\nAnswer:\nkubectl create namespace dev\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ2. Current context को default namespace dev बनाउन command के हो?\nAnswer:\nkubectl config set-context --current --namespace=dev\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ3. nginx image ko 3 replicas भएको deployment बनाउने command?\nAnswer:\nkubectl create deployment web-app --image=nginx -n dev\nkubectl scale deployment web-app --replicas=3 -n dev\n\nAlternative:\n\nkubectl create deployment web-app --image=nginx --replicas=3 -n dev\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ4. web app expose गर्न service command?\nAnswer:\nkubectl expose deployment web-app --name=web-svc --port=80 \n--target-port=80 -n dev\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ5. कुन component decides where these 3 pods will run?\nAnswer:\n\nkube-scheduler\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ6. कुन component actually node मा pod run गराउँछ?\nAnswer:\n\nkubelet, using container runtime\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ7. कुन component stores this deployment record?\nAnswer:\n\netcd\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ8. User traffic service बाट सही pod मा कसले route गर्छ?\nAnswer:\n\nkube-proxy",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
