      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Rapid Fire Mixed Questions\n\n\nQ: Namespace र Context same हुन्?\n\nA: होइन.\nNamespace = cluster भित्रको area\nContext = kubeconfig profile\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ: Pod र Container same हुन्?\n\nA: होइन.\nContainer = app box\nPod = box राख्ने smallest k8s unit\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ: Master node काम के?\n\nA: decide, manage, schedule, monitor\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ: Worker node काम के?\n\nA: actual application workload run गर्ने\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ: Deployment vs ReplicaSet?\n\nA:\nDeployment = high-level manager\nReplicaSet = pod count maintain गर्ने",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Rapid Fire Mixed Questions\n\n\nQ: Namespace र Context same हुन्?\n\nA: होइन.\nNamespace = cluster भित्रको area\nContext = kubeconfig profile\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ: Pod र Container same हुन्?\n\nA: होइन.\nContainer = app box\nPod = box राख्ने smallest k8s unit\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ: Master node काम के?\n\nA: decide, manage, schedule, monitor\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ: Worker node काम के?\n\nA: actual application workload run गर्ने\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nQ: Deployment vs ReplicaSet?\n\nA:\nDeployment = high-level manager\nReplicaSet = pod count maintain गर्ने",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
