      "updated": 1773806866307,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Final Memory Story\n\nImagine गर:\n\n    Kubernetes एउटा smart port company हो.\n\n    Head office ले सबै shipping orders API server बाट receive गर्छ.\n\n    Official data etcd मा store हुन्छ.\n\n    Scheduler ले कुन ship मा कुन cargo जाने decide गर्छ.\n\n    Each ship ko kubelet captain ले आदेश पालना गर्छ.\n\n    Container runtime ले actual cargo boxes run गर्छ.\n\n    Customers लाई stable counter दिन Service use हुन्छ.\n\n    Traffic सही ठाउँमा पुर्‍याउन kube-proxy हुन्छ.\n\n    Different business areas लाई manage गर्न Namespaces हुन्छन्.\n\n    Admin haru ko access profile लाई Context भनिन्छ.\n\n    If any cargo gets lost, controllers and ReplicaSets \n            automatically replace it.\n    \n    \n    ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Final Memory Story\n\nImagine गर:\n\n    Kubernetes एउटा smart port company हो.\n\n    Head office ले सबै shipping orders API server बाट receive गर्छ.\n\n    Official data etcd मा store हुन्छ.\n\n    Scheduler ले कुन ship मा कुन cargo जाने decide गर्छ.\n\n    Each ship ko kubelet captain ले आदेश पालना गर्छ.\n\n    Container runtime ले actual cargo boxes run गर्छ.\n\n    Customers लाई stable counter दिन Service use हुन्छ.\n\n    Traffic सही ठाउँमा पुर्‍याउन kube-proxy हुन्छ.\n\n    Different business areas लाई manage गर्न Namespaces हुन्छन्.\n\n    Admin haru ko access profile लाई Context भनिन्छ.\n\n    If any cargo gets lost, controllers and ReplicaSets \n            automatically replace it.\n    \n    \n    ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
